OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be mainly dry and
OL,6,Fcloudy with only a small chance of
OL,7,Fsome occasional brightness. Patchy
OL,8,Frain at times, more likely through the
OL,9,Fafternoon. Mild.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FCloud and rain clearing
OL,12,Fnortheast through the evening. This
OL,13,Fallowing a few clear spells and the
OL,14,Fodd shower to follow through the rest
OL,15,Fof the night.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
