OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FA mostly dry start with some
OL,6,Fbright spells. Turning cloudier
OL,7,Fthrough the middle of the day before
OL,8,Fbecoming clearer again by evening.
OL,9,FLargely dry, chance of some showers in
OL,10,Fwest.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FMainly
OL,13,Fdry on Friday, chance of rain for a
OL,14,Ftime in the afternoon. Dry and bright
OL,15,Ffor most of Saturday, some rain later.
OL,16,FVariable cloud but mainly dry Sunday.
